<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1908-08-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1908-08-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="82" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d82">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 774/281.</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Jay</persName> to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Tokyo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-08-10"><hi rend="italic">August 10,
                                1908</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Your telegram July 21: Tsunejiro Miyaoka, councilor of embassy; Dr.
                            Yoshizumi Tahara, expert, home department; Tomoye Takagi, expert,
                            government of Formosa, have to-day been appointed commissioners.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Jay.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>